astrofind (0.9.0~beta-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Beta release: all features complete, pending real-world FITS validation.
  * Version bumped from 0.5.0 to 0.9.0-beta.
  * Fixed: invert/flip broken in blink mode (precomputed image path).
  * Fixed: QSpinBox/QComboBox button widths inconsistent between themes.
  * Fixed: overlay marking colors did not match catalog table colors.
  * Added: Theme::dp() for DPI-proportional sizing across screens.
  * Added: Theme::mark*() color constants as single source of truth.
  * Fixed: 10 truncated PT-BR translations (token-limit AI generation bug).

 -- Petrus Silva Costa <petrinhu@astrofind.app>  Sat, 22 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
